SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast(sum ( LGCC_AMOUNTC ) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum ( LGCC_AMOUNTH ) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/LGCC where LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 and LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 and LGCC_LDGR_NO = :4 and LGCC_LDGR_NO > 0 and LGCC_CURRENCY = ':5' for fetch only optimize for 100 rows

select cast(sum(INUD_INTERESTAMOUNTC * (days(INUD_DATEUNTIL) - days(':2')) / (days(INUD_DATEUNTIL) - days(INUD_DATEFROM) + 1)) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(INUD_INTERESTAMOUNTH * (days(INUD_DATEUNTIL) - days(':2')) / (days(INUD_DATEUNTIL) - days(INUD_DATEFROM) + 1)) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/INUD join :1/INVO on INVO_ADMNO = :3 and INVO_CLNTNO = :4 where INUD_INVO_NO = INVO_NO and INUD_DATEBOOKING <= ':2' and INUD_DATEUNTIL > ':2' for fetch only

select LGCC_AMOUNTH, LGCC_AMOUNTC, LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO, LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO, LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO, LGCC_CURRENCY from :1/LGCC, :1/ADML where ADML_LEDGERNO = LGCC_LDGR_NO and ADML_ADMN_NO = LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO and ADML_LTYP_TYPE = 37 and LGCC_LDGR_NO > 0 and LGCC_DATE between :2 and :3 and LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO in (11, 12, 13, 14) and LGCC_AMOUNTC <> 0 for fetch only

select LGCC_AMOUNTH, LGCC_AMOUNTC, LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO, LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO, LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO, LGCC_CURRENCY from :1/LGCC, :1/ADML where ADML_LEDGERNO = LGCC_LDGR_NO and ADML_ADMN_NO = LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO and ADML_LTYP_TYPE = 39 and LGCC_LDGR_NO > 0 and LGCC_DATE between :2 and :3 and LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO in (11, 12, 13, 14) and LGCC_AMOUNTC <> 0 for fetch only
